label: Segment
desc: segment of the original description of the entity in the clinical trial eligibility criteria source text

label: Concept ID
desc: mapped concept ID in the standard vocabulary of the entity

label: Concept Name
desc: mapped concept name in the standard vocabulary of the entity

label: Start Position
desc: the position in the criteria source text where the entity starts

label: End Position
desc: the position in the criteria source text where the entity ends

label: Temporal Attribute
desc: segment of the corresponded temporal attribute of the entity in original criteria text

label: Normalized Temporal Attribute
desc: normalized temporal attribute as the number of days

label: Numerical Attribute
desc: segment of the corresponded numerical attribute of the entity in original criteria text

label: Lower Bound
desc: lower bound of the normalized numerical attribute

label: Upper Bound
desc: upper bound of the normalized numerical attribute

label: Criteria Type
desc: 1' for exclusion criteria and '0' for inclusion criteria
